##HOW TO MAKE INSTAGRAM ACCOUNT 
The main method used in clipping is called the Reposting Page Method.
In this method, you create multiple Instagram pages across different niches and post short-form content (Reels) according to the campaign you are participating in. 
Instead of relying on a single page, you prepare multiple niche-based pages so you can quickly use them whenever a relevant campaign appears.
If at any time there is no active campaign in a particular niche, you can stay consistent by repurposing clips from other pages this method is called repurpose clip method ( explained in deatil further in other files )


Niche based page strategy - 
You should always create separate pages for different niches instead of mixing everything on one page.
👉 Not having niche-based pages and posting every type of content on a single page is one of the biggest mistakes clippers make, and it significantly slows down growth.
Audiences are niche-specific. For example, someone interested in movie clips may not be interested in gym or fitness content. Mixing niches confuses the algorithm and reduces reach.
👉 Example:
If you have a page in the movie niche, you can directly use it when a movie-related campaign becomes available. And use repurpose clip method when no campagin is available in the niche.


